Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.80,0:01:48.59,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,不器用でぎこちないほど
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.01,0:01:51.59,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,愛しく始まるの？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.89,0:01:53.70,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,give me an answer
