Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.75,0:21:59.02,ENJP,NTP,0,0,0,,真っ直ぐに歩いてきた
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.68,0:22:07.10,ENJP,NTP,0,0,0,,不器用なこの心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.93,0:22:21.62,ENJP,NTP,0,0,0,,偽りないその目に映る暖かい光りを
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.62,0:22:26.67,ENJP,NTP,0,0,0,,溢れる希望の中で今僕ら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.94,0:22:32.12,ENJP,NTP,0,0,0,,どれだけの愛に出逢えるのだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.12,0:22:38.93,ENJP,NTP,0,0,0,,同じ時を今生きている愛すると
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.24,0:22:44.27,ENJP,NTP,0,0,0,,思う喜び に触れて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.75,0:21:59.02,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,筆直地一路走來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.68,0:22:07.10,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,我這顆笨拙的心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.93,0:22:21.62,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,感受著你的真誠雙眼所發出的溫暖光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.62,0:22:26.67,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,沐浴在滿溢而出的希望中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.94,0:22:32.12,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,我們究竟能遇見多深沉的愛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.12,0:22:38.93,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,一起活在當下 愛在此時
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.24,0:22:44.27,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,如此想來 不禁欣喜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.37,0:00:06.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快看 那個人好帥哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.26,0:00:07.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟糕 各種向往啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.49,0:00:09.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帥成那樣也算很少見了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.19,0:00:10.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要不要試著搭個話呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.50,0:00:12.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他絕對不會甩我們的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.36,0:00:15.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快看 那個人好像很強耶
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.10,0:00:16.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟糕 各種向往啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.56,0:00:18.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,壯成那樣也算很少見了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.21,0:00:19.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要不要試著挑戰下呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.36,0:00:21.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你絕對不是他對手啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.54,0:00:26.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 阿砂
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.25,0:00:28.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來在同一班電車上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.85,0:00:29.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都沒發現呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.21,0:00:31.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我倒是能看到你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.44,0:00:35.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朋友？好意外
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.98,0:02:09.91,title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,475)}我的男友
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.77,0:02:13.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是剛田猛男 高一
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.56,0:02:16.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這傢夥是我的朋友砂川誠
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.32,0:02:18.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們倆三歲就認識了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.51,0:02:27.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿砂 春天來了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.84,0:02:28.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.24,0:02:32.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日本迎來了春天 而我也一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.41,0:02:36.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我此生第一次交上了女朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.99,0:02:41.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,春天真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.34,0:02:43.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦喲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.81,0:02:46.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誰讓你走路總朝著天上看
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.38,0:03:00.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 等..
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.89,0:03:03.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的小寶寶啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.92,0:03:07.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他只是要幫你搬上去而已
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.22,0:03:12.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？啊..有勞了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.80,0:03:13.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.87,0:03:14.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,十分感謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.14,0:03:17.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的幫了我大忙 非常感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.83,0:03:17.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我可什麼都沒幹
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.75,0:03:18.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,路上請小心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.96,0:03:21.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 十分感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.63,0:03:24.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的十分感謝 幫大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.09,0:03:26.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常感謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.30,0:03:29.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猛男同學
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.81,0:03:32.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猛男同學 好有力氣哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.77,0:03:38.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今年的春天..是春天
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.98,0:03:44.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 是大和做的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.92,0:03:48.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 這次第一次挑戰了和式點心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.02,0:03:51.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我覺得櫻花花瓣什麼的很可愛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.78,0:03:57.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好吃！！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.01,0:04:00.06,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}嗓門太大了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.76,0:03:59.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和式點心也好好吃 大和
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.71,0:04:00.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.79,0:04:04.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我啊 最喜歡聽猛男同學的誇獎了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.45,0:04:10.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好喜歡她
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.16,0:04:16.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,春天來了呢 春天真好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.59,0:04:19.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我剛才也這麼想呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.36,0:04:23.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？真的？是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.98,0:04:24.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏天也不錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.36,0:04:26.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 夏天也很棒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.43,0:04:28.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,秋天也有秋天的優點
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.01,0:04:30.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 秋天也別有風味呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.34,0:04:32.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冬天我也超愛的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.96,0:04:34.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冬天當然也很讚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.68,0:04:37.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺就算成了老爺爺老奶奶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.07,0:04:38.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們倆的對話也不會變呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.54,0:04:42.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,..這種反應？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.20,0:04:44.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說我能回去了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.59,0:04:51.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對啊 大和
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.72,0:04:54.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是能一直像現在這樣就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.27,0:05:00.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 猛男同學
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.53,0:05:01.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.15,0:05:03.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以一起用手機拍個照嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.72,0:05:04.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.17,0:05:08.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的？那我要把那個照片當待機背景
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.80,0:05:11.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像這樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.49,0:05:15.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,準備好了嗎？我要拍了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.24,0:05:16.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.33,0:05:22.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 失敗了 好緊張哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.27,0:05:26.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的心臟好像要炸了..
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.70,0:05:30.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 這次不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.60,0:05:34.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊 那個照片也給我的手機傳一份吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.04,0:05:36.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想當待機背景
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.42,0:05:36.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.55,0:05:38.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好喜歡她
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.64,0:05:42.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 我可以接嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.54,0:05:47.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 我現在在外面哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.78,0:05:51.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？嗯 對啊 和男友在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.64,0:05:55.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和男友在一起~在一起~在一起~
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.59,0:05:55.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,男友..男友..男友..
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.36,0:05:59.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,滿腔愛意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.60,0:06:05.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 為什麼和我交往會讓她這麼開心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.60,0:06:07.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.42,0:06:08.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 那個..
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.17,0:06:10.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說吧 沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.44,0:06:14.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 朋友說想要辦聯誼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.31,0:06:18.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的朋友中單身的有五人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.87,0:06:22.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她們要我把男友以及他的朋友介紹給她們
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.23,0:06:25.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.18,0:06:29.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 我懂了 只要召集我的朋友就行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.15,0:06:31.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.56,0:06:32.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.03,0:06:33.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他說可以
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.09,0:06:34.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.14,0:06:35.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才那就是你男友？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.38,0:06:37.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聲音好有磁性哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.67,0:06:39.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用擔心 大和
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.06,0:06:42.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的朋友裡男的多得是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.15,0:06:44.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猛男同學早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.45,0:06:45.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猛男 近來可好？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.13,0:06:47.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猛男 好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.14,0:06:48.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.07,0:06:49.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好 猛男
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.02,0:06:50.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 這不是猛男嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.82,0:06:50.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猛男
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.32,0:06:50.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猛男
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.90,0:06:51.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啊 猛男
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.95,0:06:54.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了？猛男
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.24,0:06:56.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,發生啥事了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.56,0:06:59.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其實呢 我交了個女朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.73,0:07:01.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們中..
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.71,0:07:02.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的假的啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.69,0:07:03.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太棒了啊 猛男
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.70,0:07:05.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猛男交上女友 超級好消息啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.92,0:07:04.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 把他捧起來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.51,0:07:12.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們之中 沒有女友的人 舉手
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.60,0:07:15.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是..
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.53,0:07:17.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想去聯誼的人 舉手
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.64,0:07:18.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 猛男要去嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.47,0:07:18.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也要去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.76,0:07:19.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也想去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.31,0:07:19.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也要
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.85,0:07:22.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猜拳吧 名額四人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.29,0:07:25.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聯誼？誒 加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.72,0:07:29.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說什麼啊 你要強制參加
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.66,0:07:33.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以是可以 但是我不怎麼會說話哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.22,0:07:33.48,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}會冷場哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.57,0:07:36.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說不定會有好姑娘哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.90,0:07:39.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她們是大和的朋友 肯定都是好女孩啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.42,0:07:41.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猛男
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.15,0:07:46.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好女孩的朋友不一定都是好女孩哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.79,0:07:51.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有可能因為她人太好才會“被交朋友”
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.31,0:07:52.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿砂..
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.18,0:07:59.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的話好難懂哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.72,0:08:05.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猛男同學
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.94,0:08:08.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這些是明天要來參加聯誼的朋友哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.45,0:08:09.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都很可愛哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.29,0:08:13.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要為大家介紹男友 我好難為情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.51,0:08:16.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大和在笑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.42,0:08:19.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無論在哪裡 大和就是大和啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.87,0:08:26.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家好 我是猛男同學的女友大和
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.16,0:08:30.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這邊幾位是和我同一個班的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.50,0:08:31.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.17,0:08:33.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.34,0:08:34.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 大家都好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.91,0:08:37.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼凜子的男友是哪位啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.30,0:08:39.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這孩子每天都在秀恩愛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.67,0:08:40.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才沒有秀恩愛啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.11,0:08:44.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你念叨男友的事情就叫秀恩愛啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.55,0:08:46.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼是哪個？哪個？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.23,0:08:47.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那 那個..
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.96,0:08:50.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是我的男友猛男
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.70,0:08:52.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.34,0:08:56.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,熊？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.66,0:08:59.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 凜子說的沒錯 長得好高哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.06,0:09:01.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還以為是熊..
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.65,0:09:04.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,..凜子說的沒錯 手好大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.52,0:09:07.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還以為是熊..
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.57,0:09:12.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.72,0:09:13.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好耶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.71,0:09:16.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,店在這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.54,0:09:22.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思 比想象中要輕
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.45,0:09:25.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不會 謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.41,0:09:26.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有力過頭了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.61,0:09:31.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在這裡堆東西真危險呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.06,0:09:33.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搬到一邊讓大家通過吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.47,0:09:37.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好強..
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.04,0:09:41.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且逃生門還上鎖了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.53,0:09:42.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟店家的人說一聲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.41,0:09:44.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種事 與其跟店家說
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.29,0:09:47.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,更要緊的是聯繫管理大樓的公司
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.53,0:09:50.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 好帥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.55,0:09:51.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿砂真聰明
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.39,0:09:52.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.29,0:09:52.52,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,熊的朋友？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.93,0:09:53.45,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,好意外
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.70,0:09:56.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 我來點飲料
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.80,0:09:58.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要點橙汁的人？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.43,0:09:58.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.39,0:10:00.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要可樂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.34,0:10:03.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個人越看越帥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.21,0:10:04.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他好像完全不說話啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.61,0:10:05.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要不要去搭話？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.63,0:10:06.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.81,0:10:10.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說 一開始我還以為那個人是凜子的男友
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.14,0:10:12.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼是那頭熊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.58,0:10:13.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.63,0:10:09.57,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,大和事先預定了嗎？好努力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.98,0:10:11.20,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？很普通啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.87,0:10:17.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猛男 你的女友真是個超級好女孩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.22,0:10:18.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了啊 猛男
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.67,0:10:20.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有種好欣慰的感覺啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.84,0:10:22.14,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,明天大家也來把他捧起來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.61,0:10:23.60,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,目標 三次
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.80,0:10:24.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這些人平白無故地怎麼這麼愛戴凜子男友啊..
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.36,0:10:26.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,飲料都有了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.72,0:10:28.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼先來乾杯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.71,0:10:31.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？沒開瓶器啊 不好意思..
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.08,0:10:33.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,開了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.62,0:10:36.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 這傢夥居然用手打開了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.10,0:10:36.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猛男好猛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.95,0:10:37.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.21,0:10:40.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才那是什麼..
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.74,0:10:39.66,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,我的也拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.39,0:10:46.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猛男 那東西不是讓你這麼開的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.25,0:10:51.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 大家都是讀女子高校對吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.42,0:10:53.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的只有女生嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.46,0:10:56.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 那確實..
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.38,0:10:57.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是沒男生呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.56,0:11:01.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別問大和的朋友這種傻問題啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.58,0:11:02.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.94,0:11:05.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,絕對不准做失禮的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.78,0:11:08.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猛男同學 沒事的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.95,0:11:14.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 你們真的都沒有男友嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.04,0:11:15.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.99,0:11:17.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,平時沒有邂逅的機會
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.66,0:11:18.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全沒有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.16,0:11:21.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說我們雖然是男女混校 還是沒有邂逅呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.19,0:11:24.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恩恩 女生都集中在受歡迎的傢夥身上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.06,0:11:28.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們啊 說到邂逅的話只有在學園祭才有可能
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.22,0:11:31.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,學園祭啊 那時候我們也能去嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.00,0:11:33.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能來啊 來吧來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.95,0:11:34.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要去要去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.31,0:11:37.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,初3的時候辦過咖啡廳呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.23,0:11:38.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咖啡廳？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.13,0:11:39.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,穿的是什麼服裝？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.19,0:11:41.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 這個問題好老土哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.65,0:11:44.17,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,我說 能坐在你那邊嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.17,0:11:44.68,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,請吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.15,0:11:46.66,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼換位子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.66,0:11:45.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大和也辦過咖啡廳嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.48,0:11:46.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是幫廚的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.27,0:11:50.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我烤了好多不同口味的磅蛋糕呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.83,0:11:53.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 好想吃吃看呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.88,0:11:55.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會做哦 我明天就做
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.29,0:11:57.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很期待哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.58,0:12:01.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你沒事可以吃下整整兩條呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.75,0:12:04.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 糟糕 隱形眼鏡歪掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.51,0:12:06.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思 我去洗手間弄一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.40,0:12:07.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.69,0:12:09.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.47,0:12:20.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菜菜子和小步還不回來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.00,0:12:23.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去看一下她們哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.51,0:12:25.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.29,0:12:28.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,廁所在哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.86,0:12:29.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.65,0:12:32.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再怎麼說塊頭也太大了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.39,0:12:34.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.66,0:12:36.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那樣的男友怎麼行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.70,0:12:38.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差點就不能算人類了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.92,0:12:43.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凜子她每天都一直說男友怎麼怎麼帥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.24,0:12:45.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我還以為是什麼樣的大帥哥呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.22,0:12:47.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那算什麼啊 真的嚇死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.37,0:12:48.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,簡直是大猩猩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.73,0:12:51.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可沒勇氣跟他走在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.41,0:12:55.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好女孩的朋友不一定都是好女孩哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.72,0:13:00.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然說他帥 凜子沒搞錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.34,0:13:06.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凜..凜子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.86,0:13:17.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猛男同學他..
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.34,0:13:22.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很帥啊 超級帥的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.13,0:13:29.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大和
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.15,0:13:39.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大和
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.76,0:13:41.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大和
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.98,0:13:48.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起 猛男同學 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.13,0:13:49.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你道歉什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.40,0:13:54.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為朋友對猛男同學說了壞話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.96,0:13:58.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猛男同學一定很傷心吧 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.77,0:14:00.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才沒有傷心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.47,0:14:02.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.20,0:14:06.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大和 沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.91,0:14:09.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人各有別啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.00,0:14:13.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不用擔心我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.58,0:14:16.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,傷心的是你才對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.74,0:14:19.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正因為每個人都是不同的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.13,0:14:23.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才遇見了你 大和
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.04,0:14:29.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到你哭我會很難過的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.46,0:14:35.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有傷心？真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.61,0:14:36.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毫髮無傷
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.40,0:14:43.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說回來 大和在朋友面前誇了我很多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.76,0:14:45.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.44,0:14:50.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猛男同學真厲害呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.61,0:14:56.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我果然很喜歡猛男同學啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.10,0:15:01.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的非常..非常喜歡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.79,0:15:08.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊 一定是我的說明方式不對
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.77,0:15:10.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,講得太含糊了所以沒聽懂呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.21,0:15:12.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猛男同學的帥氣之處
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.90,0:15:13.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大和
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.12,0:15:16.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回去之後會簡單易懂地解釋給大家聽的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.42,0:15:19.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我倒是無所謂啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.04,0:15:20.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 我想告訴她們
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.10,0:15:24.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為大家只是不認識真正的猛男君而已
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.72,0:15:26.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大和
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.54,0:15:29.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我每天都會想的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.98,0:15:31.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,“和大和相遇太好了”
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.34,0:15:35.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,“要是這樣的日子一直持續下去就好了”
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.89,0:15:39.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,失火啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.38,0:15:43.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿砂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.15,0:15:45.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猛男
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.36,0:15:47.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然就失火了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.51,0:15:49.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然打給消防局了 不過消防隊還沒有來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.08,0:15:49.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凜子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.81,0:15:51.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家呢？大家都在嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.09,0:15:52.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼辦？菜菜子和小步不在
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.70,0:15:55.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她們一直沒從廁所回來 還在大樓裡..
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.78,0:16:02.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在這裡等著 我一定帶她們出來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.96,0:16:03.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猛男同學
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.29,0:16:07.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大和 你別擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.87,0:16:10.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定會救出你的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.96,0:16:21.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猛男 猛男
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.56,0:16:23.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.13,0:16:23.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菜菜子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.91,0:16:24.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救護車
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.03,0:16:26.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事的 我已經叫了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.74,0:16:27.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.32,0:16:34.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有種..被非常強力的野獸..抬來抬去的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.89,0:16:36.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是猛男同學啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.26,0:16:40.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大和
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.75,0:16:43.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在大和發過來的照片之中
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.34,0:16:46.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你開心地笑著
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.08,0:16:49.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都是好朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.52,0:16:54.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,林檎..對不起 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.00,0:16:56.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事吧 振作一點
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.96,0:17:03.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,站得起來嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.06,0:17:04.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.05,0:17:05.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快走
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.39,0:17:07.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快走
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.96,0:17:11.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快走！！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.63,0:17:23.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小步
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.81,0:17:24.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.43,0:17:25.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,消防隊還沒來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.57,0:17:27.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這可糟了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.97,0:17:26.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凜子..
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.22,0:17:28.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.25,0:17:29.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 你男友他..
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.43,0:17:31.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能不妙了..
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.51,0:17:36.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他為了救我..被留在裡面了..
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.23,0:17:44.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是..到此為止了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.74,0:17:50.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回想起來 最近我實在是幸福過頭了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.92,0:17:53.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猛男同學..
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.26,0:17:55.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大和 多虧了你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.15,0:17:57.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猛男同學
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.76,0:18:01.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果能為你而死的話 這一生也算不錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.23,0:18:12.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手機？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.88,0:18:13.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能撥通嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.21,0:18:17.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猛男 聽得見嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.07,0:18:19.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽我說 大和同學她
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.42,0:18:22.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在一副恨不得衝進大火裡的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.02,0:18:27.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猛男同學 放開我 讓我去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.96,0:18:31.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猛男同學 猛男同學
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.61,0:18:30.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以呢 你能不能趕緊快點回來？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.23,0:18:34.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要 猛男同學
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.56,0:18:38.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猛男同學 拜託..
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.78,0:18:41.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要 猛男..
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.44,0:18:36.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不在的話 我會很無聊的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.94,0:18:39.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猛男 喂 你聽見了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.93,0:18:49.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別哭 大和
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.58,0:18:52.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要為了我哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.86,0:18:54.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不需要擔心我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.61,0:18:55.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快露出笑容吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.59,0:18:59.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到你哭我最難過了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.60,0:19:01.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大和
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.33,0:19:05.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我..會活下去的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.19,0:19:09.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,活著..用這雙手..
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.17,0:19:25.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓大和幸福！！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.22,0:19:31.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猛男同學
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.87,0:19:37.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猛男同學..
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.91,0:19:44.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猛男同學
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.09,0:19:50.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大和 我發誓不會再讓你哭泣了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.39,0:20:04.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個..十分感謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.10,0:20:08.78,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}心動
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.07,0:20:11.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼？怦然心動什麼的..吊橋效應嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.96,0:20:12.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.91,0:20:14.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是我的類型啦 完全不是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.60,0:20:19.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個哦 關於猛男同學的帥氣之處
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.50,0:20:21.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我覺得是我的說法不太對
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.24,0:20:25.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個哦 簡單解釋猛男同學的帥氣之處的話..
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.69,0:20:27.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用啦 我們已經明白了啦 凜子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.68,0:20:31.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說 對不起 是我們錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.50,0:20:33.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的男友是個好男人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.69,0:20:35.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而你也是個好女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.42,0:20:36.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.62,0:20:37.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不准搶哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.10,0:20:38.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才不會啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.60,0:20:40.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說也搶不來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.07,0:20:43.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他眼裡根本只有你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.89,0:20:48.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我覺得除了老死之外 你根本死不掉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.99,0:20:49.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.63,0:20:54.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是猛男果然猛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.06,0:20:55.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又愛上你啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.02,0:20:56.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猛男最棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.24,0:20:57.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好嘞 捧他起來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.93,0:20:59.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 預備..
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.60,0:21:07.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猛男同學 今天真的謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.84,0:21:10.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家好像都明白了你的優點哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.47,0:21:14.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天猛男同學也好帥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.80,0:21:17.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是當上消防員的話 一定會有神勇表現吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.64,0:21:20.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然會讓人很擔心..
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.24,0:21:23.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚安 猛男同學 明天見
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.44,0:21:32.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是春天呢 春天真好啊 大和
